short_summary: Procurement of 16 All-Terrain Vehicle (ATV) Youth, 2x4 4 Stroke Gasoline Engine for delivery to CFB Gander, NFLD
description: The Department of National Defence (DND) has a requirement to procure sixteen (16) All-Terrain Vehicle (ATV) Youth, 2x4 4 Stroke Gasoline Engine for delivery to Canadian Forces Base (CFB) Gander, NFLD. The requested delivery date is 240 days. The Crown retains the rights to negotiate with suppliers on any procurement.
